  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The first-ever trial of a senior Syrian government official began in April, 2020 in Koblenz, Germany. Since the start, SJAC&apos;s trial monitor has attended each trial session, and SJAC has published high-quality trial monitoring reports in English and Arabic. These reports create a historical record of this groundbreaking trial and provide access to Syrian victims and witnesses interested in following the proceedings from afar.</narrative>
